#: pisi/cli/build.py:15
msgid ""
"Build eopkg packages\n"
"\n"
"Usage: build [<pspec.xml> | <sourcename>] ...\n"
"\n"
"You can give a URI of the pspec.xml file. eopkg will\n"
"fetch all necessary files and build the package for you.\n"
"\n"
"Alternatively, you can give the name of a source package\n"
"to be downloaded from a repository containing sources.\n"
msgstr ""
"Construcció de paquets eopkg\n"
"\n"
"Ús: build [<pspec.xml> | <sourcename>] ...\n"
"\n"
"Podeu especificar l'URI del fitxer pspec.xml. L'eopkg\n"
"obtindrà tots els fitxers necessaris i us construirà el paquet.\n"
"\n"
"Alternativament, podeu especificar el nom del paquet font\n"
"per baixar d'un repositori que contingui fonts.\n"

#: pisi/cli/build.py:38
msgid "build options"
msgstr "opcions de construcció"

#: pisi/cli/build.py:49
